name: Eva Elfie
description:
Eva Elfie (May 27, 2000) is a Russian adult model and glamour model, best known for her work with Playboy Plus. She has been featured in Playboy editorial spreads and has appeared on the cover of the magazine. She is also active on her personal Instagram account, where she shares photos of her modeling work and her personal life.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Another one for today! A textual inversion of Eva Elfie. I used 70 public images of her, with a 6300 steps training process. Hope you'll like it! To use it in your works:

  • this one is particularly horny 😂 check the examples for some inspiration about the prompt;

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add evaelfie00 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 30, CFG between 7 and 8 seems to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision. Check the gallery for some inspiration!

Have fun!
